of that book. I didn't know he wrote it. I think, but it's been on my reading list to get... I've

01:33:55.680 --> 01:34:02.400
been trying to get a good balanced reading list about the COVID pandemic to understand what the

01:34:02.400 --> 01:34:09.920
hell happened. And anytime I start to try to go into that place, I'm exhausted by it. Well,

01:34:09.920 --> 01:34:15.520
it's interesting to me that you wouldn't wait longer before delving into those books to have

