know. Everything from the scientists to the political leaders. It felt like the blog posts and

01:35:12.720 --> 01:35:17.360
the tweets didn't quite cap it. They didn't quite cap it. No, one of the things I read a ton,

01:35:17.360 --> 01:35:24.080
I don't read any modern political books, so I don't read the memoirs of elected officials.

