about it recently, she said, I didn't mean it. I was just trying to impress Russell Brand.

01:37:51.120 --> 01:37:55.440
I don't know if I'm more bothered by the thing she first said or by the fact that she wanted to

01:37:55.440 --> 01:38:01.200
impress Russell Brand. But it's just like, it's just really not for me. And I agree with her on,

01:38:01.200 --> 01:38:06.400
