01:40:49.600 --> 01:40:55.360
democratic, through the voting process. But I'm just annoyed how little technology there is in

01:40:55.360 --> 01:41:00.720
the whole process, how little innovation there is in the whole process, all of this.

01:41:00.720 --> 01:41:07.200
