01:41:07.200 --> 01:41:14.160
hobbyism. And I think there's a good chance that some of the people in my audience are political

01:41:14.160 --> 01:41:21.200
hobbyists in the sense that they follow this stuff as entertainment to some degree. And I've written

01:41:21.200 --> 01:41:27.280
a lot about how... I've read a lot and talked a lot about how, okay, we vote every two years or

01:41:27.280 --> 01:41:32.000
every four years in our local elections, et cetera. And then we think about politics all the time.

01:41:32.640 --> 01:41:37.520
Neil Postman wrote about this in his book, Amusing Ourselves to Death. But what are you actually

01:41:37.520 --> 01:41:43.120
going to do about the kids starving in this country and the nuclear buildup in that country?

01:41:43.120 --> 01:41:48.480
