01:41:48.480 --> 01:41:53.520
any number, it could mean the town or city you live in, or it might mean an athletic club or

01:41:53.600 --> 01:41:58.160
whatever. If everybody, this time they spent on political hobbyism, they moved somewhere else,

01:41:58.160 --> 01:42:01.440
which might put me out of a job, that's okay. I'm willing to lose my job because I think it

01:42:01.440 --> 01:42:06.160
would be so beneficial. Then our communities would just be that much better, because you can

01:42:06.160 --> 01:42:10.560
actually affect change in a much more tangible way locally, whether it's... People talk about

01:42:10.560 --> 01:42:17.120
potholes, but other things as well. Yeah. And I wish our system was more amenable to that kind

01:42:17.120 --> 01:42:23.440
of contribution, hopefully through the digital space it would be. Let me ask you about on the

