02:52:17.520 --> 02:52:23.600
interesting, things I want to talk about, and things where it's being discussed at one layer

02:52:23.600 --> 02:52:28.640
and I want to go deeper on it and I feel like I'm able to do that. I choose those stories in the

02:52:28.640 --> 02:52:33.120
