03:00:59.440 --> 03:01:03.920
Something you've thought about, spoken about for quite a time. Do you think we'll ever see peace

03:01:03.920 --> 03:01:08.720
in this part of the world? I don't know. I mean, I could say yes.

03:01:08.720 --> 03:01:09.840
That's an honest answer.

03:01:09.840 --> 03:01:17.360
I could say yes. One of the problems is, and I'll give, you may not know that

03:01:18.320 --> 03:01:23.760
there are people on the left of my audience who call me a Netanyahu shill,

03:01:24.400 --> 03:01:30.000
even though I've never been a supporter of Netanyahu and I'm on the left. I just don't think

03:01:30.000 --> 03:01:37.920
that some of the kind of black and white characterizations about Israel are even remotely

03:01:37.920 --> 03:01:43.520
accurate. And I think most people, it's become a sort of litmus test. Are you criticizing Israel

03:01:43.520 --> 03:01:46.960
enough? Are you showing us that you're actually left-wing? I don't do any of that stuff.

03:01:46.960 --> 03:01:49.200
