Putin may have seen himself as having other tools with which to try to

03:05:44.480 --> 03:05:50.800
expand influence that may have been different than geographic pursuits, geographic pursuits.

03:05:51.680 --> 03:05:59.680
But we don't know that for sure. I also have a really hard time imagining what the end of this

03:05:59.680 --> 03:06:09.840
looks like. That's very scary because sometimes the most benign end seems to be that Putin ends

