that latter is super likely. The former, there's reports about his health. I don't know how accurate

03:06:23.520 --> 03:06:31.280
they are. It's just hard to imagine a face-saving exit that is going to be even remotely...

03:06:32.800 --> 03:06:38.640
What's the word? It's not even a question of acceptable. It's not satisfying either. Just

